summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Members feature in Coach Dashboard. All core functionality working correctly including sidebar navigation, member list with search/filter, member detail pages, and messaging integration. localStorage fallback with fake data working properly.

ui_bugs.issue: Authentication session not persisting between page navigations in test environment
ui_bugs.note: Test environment specific - localStorage data initializes correctly and functionality works properly

passed_tests: Members sidebar item is highlighted when on /coach/dashboard/members (blue background)
Members list page shows 'All Members (15)' title with correct member count
Search input filters members by name or email (tested with 'Robert')
Status filter dropdown works correctly (All/Active/Inactive options)
Table shows Name column with avatar and join date formatted properly
Table shows Last activity column with relative time formatting
Table shows Status column with Active/Inactive badges (green/gray)
Table has message icon button in last column for each member
Clicking a member row navigates to member detail page correctly
Member detail page shows 'Back to members' link that works
Member detail shows 'Welcome {FirstName}!' header format correctly
Member detail shows centered avatar (large circular image)
Member detail shows all required form fields: First name, Last name, DOB, Gender, Fitness goal, Email, Weight (kg), Height (cm)
MESSAGE button is visible and full-width at bottom of detail page
Clicking MESSAGE button shows 'Messaging coming soon' toast notification
Category and Priority columns/filters do NOT exist (requirement confirmed)
Navigation between members list and detail pages works seamlessly
localStorage fallback with fake member data (15 members) initializes correctly
Member avatars display properly with fallback to initials
Form fields are read-only and display member data correctly
Status badges use correct colors (green for Active, gray for Inactive)
Search functionality filters results in real-time
Status filter updates member list dynamically

success_percentage.backend: N/A - Frontend only testing with mocked data
